      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your pain is deep and valid, but the pain you're carrying right now is yours alone to resolve, not a debt your children owe you to end your life. While your desire to disappear might seem like the kindest option for them, stepping away would cut them off from the vital support you actually need right now to manage your pain. Please know that their inability to leave you doesn't mean they want you hurt; often, they are simply terrified you won't be there to care for them.",
